courses.learning_outcomes:
At the conclusion of the course, you will be able to:
1. develop an understanding of the chacteristics and needs of students that require special counselling;
2. acquire essential helping and counselling skills in working with students with special needs;
3. form some basic principles to collaborate with significant others in the lives students with special needs to promote positive development.

(Individual course teachers may update the learning outcome as and whenever necessary.)

